= MaglevDNS - a programmable DNS forwarder

Not to be confused with the real "MagLev" project.

= Quick Start

1. git clone git://git.dlitz.net/maglevdns.git
2. cd maglevdns
3. rake gem
4. gem install pkg/*.gem
5. Copy one of the examples from the examples/ directory to my-script.rb
6. Edit my-script.rb
7. sudo maglevdns --script my-script.rb

